Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.57,0:00:04.99,Оригінал,Salem,0,0,0,,Legends...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.64,0:00:09.22,Оригінал,Salem,0,0,0,,Stories scattered through time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.05,0:00:16.04,Оригінал,Salem,0,0,0,,Man, born from dust, was strong, \Nwise, and resourceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:21.64,Оригінал,Salem,0,0,0,,But an inevitable darkness—creatures of\N destruction, the creatures of Grimm—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:23.75,Оригінал,Salem,0,0,0,,set their sights on man \Nand all of his creations.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.43,0:00:26.01,Оригінал,Salem,0,0,0,,When all seemed lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.01,0:00:30.23,Оригінал,Salem,0,0,0,,and it seemed man's brief \Nexistence might return to dust,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.81,0:00:34.58,Оригінал,Salem,0,0,0,,the smallest spark of hope \Nbrought forth a great light.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.80,0:00:40.28,Оригінал,Salem,0,0,0,,Once born of dust, man used \Nhis passion and ingenuity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.28,0:00:43.68,Оригінал,Salem,0,0,0,,to discover a new power, \Nappropriately called Dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.74,0:00:50.04,Оригінал,Salem,0,0,0,,Man thus lit their way through \Nthe darkness and restored civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.01,0:01:08.01,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Hey, listen Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.01,0:01:13.96,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Yang graduated from Signal Academy \Nand got accepted to Beacon Academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.96,0:01:15.71,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Isn't that great?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.71,0:01:18.68,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Sis always said she wanted to be a Huntress,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:22.04,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,and it's really happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.04,0:01:25.22,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Which is a little frustrating, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.02,0:01:27.90,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Of course I'm happy for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.90,0:01:33.05,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,but I want to be a Huntress too, \Nand my grades at Signal aren't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.05,0:01:35.77,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,What can I do to be more like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.83,0:01:42.11,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Anyway, when it comes to handling weapons, \NI know I'm as good as anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.11,0:01:43.49,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,I just gotta work harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.94,0:01:48.75,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Someday, I'll fight to protect people \Nfrom the Grimm just like you did, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.76,0:02:07.64,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Oh? Yang!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.42,0:02:13.15,Оригінал,Yang,0,0,0,,What were you talking to Mom about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.48,0:02:17.53,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,About your acceptance. I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.02,0:02:20.19,Оригінал,Yang,0,0,0,,Is that right? Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.89,0:02:39.72,Оригінал,Klein,0,0,0,,The arrangements have \Nbeen made, Mistress Weiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:45.06,Оригінал,Weiss,0,0,0,,Shall we go, Klein?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:46.63,Оригінал,Klein,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:03:03.61,Оригінал,Weiss,0,0,0,,You're drinking \Nin the daytime again, Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:13.29,Оригінал,Whitley,0,0,0,,Are you ready, Weiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:16.27,Оригінал,Weiss,0,0,0,,Whitley. Do you think you're the one testing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:20.58,Оригінал,Whitley,0,0,0,,I'm worried about you. \NA test this dangerous isn't normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:23.57,Оригінал,Whitley,0,0,0,,I'm sure you would agree, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.57,0:03:27.43,Оригінал,Weiss,0,0,0,,No. This is hardly enough to intimidate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:32.94,Оригінал,Weiss,0,0,0,,Shut up and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.47,0:03:42.31,Оригінал,Whitley,0,0,0,,I've always watched you, \Nmy fearless, foolish sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:13.24,Оригінал,Weiss,0,0,0,,I am very pleased to see you, \NFather. Elder Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:17.17,Оригінал,Weiss,0,0,0,,This is the final test, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:20.23,Оригінал,Jacques,0,0,0,,This is utterly pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.54,0:04:23.98,Оригінал,Winter,0,0,0,,Wasn't this your choice, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:25.61,Оригінал,Winter,0,0,0,,Weiss is prepared to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.24,0:04:33.08,Оригінал,Weiss,0,0,0,,Well, then, please unleash the Grimm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.08,0:04:37.88,Оригінал,Jacques,0,0,0,,Fine. But the instant I decide \Nyou can't do this, you fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:40.88,Оригінал,Jacques,0,0,0,,And that will be the end \Nof your selfish behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:42.89,Оригінал,Weiss,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:17.36,Оригінал,Whitley,0,0,0,,Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:21.19,Оригінал,Jacques,0,0,0,,Now you understand, correct?\NWe're finished here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:23.94,Оригінал,Winter,0,0,0,,No. It isn't over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.56,0:06:49.08,Оригінал,Blake,0,0,0,,Adam, are we really doing this alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.08,0:06:51.24,Оригінал,Adam,0,0,0,,The only guards will be Atlas toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:55.10,Оригінал,Adam,0,0,0,,The humans fear the White Fang \Ntoo much to face us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:58.22,Оригінал,Adam,0,0,0,,But you... are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.22,0:07:00.73,Оригінал,Blake,0,0,0,,Do you think I'm the type to scare easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:03.70,Оригінал,Adam,0,0,0,,I'm very aware of your bravery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:09.74,Оригінал,Adam,0,0,0,,That's the Company's train.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:13.85,Оригінал,Adam,0,0,0,,The entire cargo of Dust is ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:28.52,Оригінал,Adam,0,0,0,,Well, this is going to get messy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.46,0:07:35.24,Оригінал,Blake,0,0,0,,Try not to have too much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.02,0:08:09.30,Оригінал,Winter,0,0,0,,Your Aura can only take a direct attack \N once or twice at most.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:14.00,Оригінал,Winter,0,0,0,,The moment you're hit, you're finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.61,0:08:18.26,Оригінал,Winter,0,0,0,,The powerless return to dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:21.82,Оригінал,Winter,0,0,0,,That is the law of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:37.55,Оригінал,Klein,0,0,0,,Mistress Weiss, you did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:44.93,Оригінал,Weiss,0,0,0,,You will accept my enrollment \Nin Beacon Academy now, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.14,0:09:49.69,Оригінал,Winter,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.97,0:09:51.41,Оригінал,Jacques,0,0,0,,Have it your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.25,0:10:46.88,Оригінал,Adam,0,0,0,,Perfect. We'll run the train \Ninto the ravine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:51.75,Оригінал,Blake,0,0,0,,It isn't on autopilot. \NThere are human workers riding, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:56.00,Оригінал,Adam,0,0,0,,Just humans. They aren't Faunus like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:10:58.24,Оригінал,Blake,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.81,0:11:03.84,Оригінал,Adam,0,0,0,,Blake?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.57,0:11:07.60,Оригінал,Blake,0,0,0,,Farewell, Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:10.10,Оригінал,Adam,0,0,0,,Blake!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:12.77,Оригінал,Adam,0,0,0,,Are you betraying me... betraying the White Fang?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.93,0:11:17.14,Оригінал,Blake,0,0,0,,I have to find my own path.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.65,Оригінал,White Fang A,0,0,0,,Should we follow Blake?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:33.96,Оригінал,Adam,0,0,0,,Leave her be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.45,0:11:38.46,Оригінал,Adam,0,0,0,,Once she learns more about the world, \Nshe'll know we're in the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:58.49,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,I forgot the city was so big! \NIt's so much more fun than Patch Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.78,0:12:03.25,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,I can listen to music at scroll shops, \Nvisit cafés and weapon stores,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:05.36,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,and the time just flies by!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.36,0:12:09.00,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Oh, what should I do about Yang's present?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:14.56,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,The Dust shop is still open!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:26.84,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,The latest issue of {\i1}Weapon Magazine{\i0}! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:29.69,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,You can't get it on \NPatch Island until next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.69,0:12:32.15,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,The city of Vale is so advanced!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.76,0:12:37.02,Оригінал,Yang,0,0,0,,"We are delighted to accept you \Ninto Beacon Academy."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.12,0:12:43.54,Оригінал,Yang,0,0,0,,Dad, did Ruby come home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.54,0:12:45.37,Оригінал,Tai,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:48.42,Оригінал,Yang,0,0,0,,She said she'd be back in a minute. \NI wonder what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.98,0:12:52.67,Оригінал,Tai,0,0,0,,She's secretly buying a present \Nto celebrate your acceptance, Yang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.67,0:12:56.97,Оригінал,Yang,0,0,0,,Oh, why did you tell me? \NI was trying so hard to play dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.97,0:12:58.68,Оригінал,Tai,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:03.68,Оригінал,Tai,0,0,0,,We won't have as many chances \Nto go out as a family now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.16,0:13:07.54,Оригінал,Yang,0,0,0,,I wonder if Ruby will do okay with me gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.54,0:13:10.94,Оригінал,Yang,0,0,0,,When she gets excited,\Nshe loses sight of everything around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:13.44,Оригінал,Tai,0,0,0,,It's about time Ruby became independent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:15.97,Оригінал,Tai,0,0,0,,It's great that you support each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:18.78,Оригінал,Tai,0,0,0,,but it's not good for Ruby \Nif she's always depending on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.78,0:13:21.45,Оригінал,Yang,0,0,0,,Fine, fine, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:24.72,Оригінал,Tai,0,0,0,,She certainly is late, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.94,0:13:31.71,Оригінал,Store Owner,0,0,0,,Welc—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:34.34,Оригінал,Roman,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea how hard it is
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.99,0:13:38.09,Оригінал,Roman,0,0,0,,to find a dust shop open this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:44.34,Оригінал,Store Owner,0,0,0,,You can take my money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:45.99,Оригінал,Roman,0,0,0,,We're not here for your money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:47.21,Оригінал,Roman,0,0,0,,Help yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.59,0:13:55.61,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,"The first stage of a weapon's transformation
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.61,0:13:58.17,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,should combine both offensive \Nand defensive capabilities."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:13:59.29,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Yeah, totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:00.16,Оригінал,Henchman A,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.16,0:14:02.52,Оригінал,Henchman A,0,0,0,,Hey kid, put your hands in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:06.33,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:09.71,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.71,0:14:11.45,Оригінал,Henchman A,0,0,0,,Put your hands up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:14.46,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Are you robbing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.46,0:14:15.71,Оригінал,Henchman A,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.10,0:14:20.17,Оригінал,Henchman B,0,0,0,,You punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.01,0:14:26.11,Оригінал,Roman,0,0,0,,A Semblance?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.11,0:14:28.52,Оригінал,Roman,0,0,0,,A Beacon Academy student?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:10.85,Оригінал,Roman,0,0,0,,You were worth every cent. Truly, you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:15.23,Оригінал,Roman,0,0,0,,Well, Red, I think we can all say it's been an eventful evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:19.73,Оригінал,Roman,0,0,0,,And as much as I'd love to stick around,\NI'm afraid this is where we part ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.30,0:15:35.68,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:38.71,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,You thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:50.39,Оригінал,Roman,0,0,0,,Persistent...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.46,0:15:59.81,Оригінал,Tai,0,0,0,,She's nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:02.03,Оригінал,Yang,0,0,0,,Ruby, you're all over the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:07.77,Оригінал,Tai,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:10.03,Оригінал,Yang,0,0,0,,Ruby, what did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.36,0:16:39.61,Оригінал,Roman,0,0,0,,We got a Huntress. Let's beat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:55.30,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Wow! You're a Huntress?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.15,0:17:04.84,Оригінал,Glynda,0,0,0,,Miss, did you not stop to think about \Nhow your actions put others in great danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:09.59,Оригінал,Glynda,0,0,0,,Is your Aura strong enough \Nto stop every bullet they fired?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:12.85,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,But they...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:17.71,Оригінал,Police A,0,0,0,,Oh, Professor Ozpin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.71,0:17:19.85,Оригінал,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Just stopping by for a quick visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.16,0:17:22.47,Оригінал,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Good evening, Tai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:27.42,Оригінал,Tai,0,0,0,,Professor! I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:28.86,Оригінал,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:32.87,Оригінал,Ozpin,0,0,0,,I just want to speak \Nwith your daughter a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:39.01,Оригінал,Yang,0,0,0,,Hey, was that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:39.87,Оригінал,Tai,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:43.13,Оригінал,Tai,0,0,0,,The head of Beacon Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.38,0:17:47.17,Оригінал,Glynda,0,0,0,,There's someone here \Nwho would like to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.93,0:17:56.56,Оригінал,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Ruby Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:02.76,Оригінал,Ozpin,0,0,0,,You have silver eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.34,0:18:05.77,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Um, you are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:08.34,Оригінал,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Do you know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.34,0:18:10.43,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Yes, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.95,0:18:12.59,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Professor Ozpin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:15.28,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,You're the headmaster at Beacon Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.29,0:18:19.29,Оригінал,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you. Now, a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:24.29,Оригінал,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Do you want to attend my school?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.55,0:18:25.29,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.29,0:18:27.92,Оригінал,Yang,0,0,0,,Unbelievable! Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.41,0:18:32.94,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Yeah. He said he'd let me \Nskip two grades to get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:37.31,Оригінал,Yang,0,0,0,,Amazing! Now we can enroll together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.52,0:18:43.75,Оригінал,Ozpin,0,0,0,,She's gifted. She reminds me \Nof your Team STRQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.75,0:18:45.81,Оригінал,Tai,0,0,0,,Ruby is still a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.33,0:18:48.32,Оригінал,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Children eventually leave the nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.95,0:18:52.99,Оригінал,Tai,0,0,0,,I never dreamed they'd both leave together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.91,0:19:13.60,Оригінал,Blake,0,0,0,,"Notice of acceptance..."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.11,0:19:19.79,Оригінал,Blake,0,0,0,,Now I can take a different path.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.58,0:19:25.28,Оригінал,Klein,0,0,0,,Your remaining luggage \Nhas been sent to Beacon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:27.27,Оригінал,Weiss,0,0,0,,Thanks. I'd better go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:29.90,Оригінал,Klein,0,0,0,,Why don't you wait a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.63,0:19:34.87,Оригінал,Weiss,0,0,0,,Winter was too busy to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:38.28,Оригінал,Weiss,0,0,0,,Father and Whitley couldn't \Nbe bothered to see me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:39.92,Оригінал,Weiss,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:43.83,Оригінал,Weiss,0,0,0,,But I'm happy that you came, Klein.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.83,0:19:45.54,Оригінал,Weiss,0,0,0,,Please be well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:48.71,Оригінал,Klein,0,0,0,,You too, Mistress. \NPlease take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.71,0:19:50.77,Оригінал,Klein,0,0,0,,I am certain you will become a fine Huntress
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.77,0:19:53.09,Оригінал,Klein,0,0,0,,and will carry on the legacy \Nof Master Nicholas,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:56.30,Оригінал,Klein,0,0,0,,as a descendant of the great Schnee family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.30,0:19:58.36,Оригінал,Klein,0,0,0,,I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.65,0:20:12.74,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,I'm going, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.86,0:20:25.33,Оригінал,Blake,0,0,0,,Phew! I made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.31,0:20:35.96,Оригінал,Weiss,0,0,0,,Phew... I made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.85,0:20:42.10,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Thanks, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:46.06,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,For you and Mom and Uncle \Nand my teachers...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:50.86,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,And... I'll be as good as the best Huntsmen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.86,0:20:53.31,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,I'll become a super awesome Huntress,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:55.36,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,and I'll make tons of friends, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.84,0:20:58.45,Оригінал,Tai,0,0,0,,That's the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.45,0:21:01.37,Оригінал,Tai,0,0,0,,But you don't need to \Noverdo it trying to be the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.97,0:21:07.12,Оригінал,Tai,0,0,0,,You two should just stay \Nthe way you are. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:10.92,Оригінал,Yang,0,0,0,,All right, Dad! We should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.92,0:21:12.88,Оригінал,Tai,0,0,0,,Write to me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.28,0:21:14.27,Оригінал,Ruby,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.27,0:21:15.49,Оригінал,Yang,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.21,0:21:31.89,Оригінал,Salem,0,0,0,,Through battle, man won life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.65,0:21:35.90,Оригінал,Salem,0,0,0,,But even the most brilliant lights \Neventually flicker and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.90,0:21:37.55,Оригінал,Salem,0,0,0,,And then... \Ndarkness will return.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.27,0:21:41.97,Оригінал,Salem,0,0,0,,So stay vigilant, guardians \Nof the light, but take heed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.66,0:21:46.41,Оригінал,Salem,0,0,0,,There will be no victory in strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.94,0:21:52.57,Оригінал,Ozpin,0,0,0,,But perhaps victory is in the simpler things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.67,0:21:58.03,Оригінал,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Things that are long forgotten...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.03,0:22:02.64,Оригінал,Ozpin,0,0,0,,Things that require a smaller, more honest soul.
